    "username": "emollick",
    "nickname": "Ethan Mollick",
    "text": "Interestingly, Google no longer has a public frontier model. They have a very good flash model, but a very good flash model can't do frontier work without a good frontier orchestrator.\n\nI am sure this will change soon, but Gemini 3.1 Pro is very clearly lagging at this point.",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/emollick/status/2067617541762031900",
    "time": "2026-06-18 22:36",
    "created_at": "Thu Jun 18 14:36:51 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2067617541762031900",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "emollick",
    "nickname": "Ethan Mollick",
    "text": "A very good flash model may be all you need for mass serving consumers, but it doesn't do much for serious or agentic work.",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/emollick/status/2067618024480186707",
    "time": "2026-06-18 22:38",
    "created_at": "Thu Jun 18 14:38:46 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2067618024480186707",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "emollick",
    "nickname": "Ethan Mollick",
    "text": "Its also a shame because Google has some of the most innovative AI apps, like NotebookLM, but they need smarter brains to power them (as well as the harnesses needed for those brains)",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/emollick/status/2067620594221298007",
    "time": "2026-06-18 22:48",
    "created_at": "Thu Jun 18 14:48:58 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2067620594221298007",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "emollick",
    "nickname": "Ethan Mollick",
    "text": "Among all the big hires the labs are making recently recently, and since people occasionally ask, it may be worth reiterating that I do not take money from any of the AI labs. I also don't take any corporate sponsorship money for anything I write, whether here or substack, etc.",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/emollick/status/2067640755846291811",
    "time": "2026-06-19 00:09",
    "created_at": "Thu Jun 18 16:09:05 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2067640755846291811",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "emollick",
    "nickname": "Ethan Mollick",
    "text": "This is not a dig at the people who join the labs. I talk to leaders at the big AI companies regularly, That’s where a lot of the most interesting work is happening, and, if I was in a different field, I would be much more tempted to go where the hard problems are.",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/emollick/status/2067644788564709615",
    "time": "2026-06-19 00:25",
    "created_at": "Thu Jun 18 16:25:07 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2067644788564709615",
    "is_retweet": false
